description: HCAL is designed to track 1.25x the returns of the Solactive Equal Weight Canada Banks Index, investing in Canadian banks — using modest 25% cash leverage. HCAL does not use derivatives.*Effective April 14, 2023, the investment objective of the Hamilton Enhanced Canadian Bank ETF (HCAL) was changed. Please refer to the disclosure documents of HCAL at www.hamiltonetfs.com.
name: Hamilton Enhanced Canadian Bank ETF
